Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.86,0:00:04.88,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,なんば　むった\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:06.55,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hello? Aunt Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:07.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンおばちゃん！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:07.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…ちょっと！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:07.23,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:11.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[ｹｲﾀｲ](ｼｬﾛﾝ)\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:11.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ～ ごめんなさい｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:11.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケータイ 落としちゃった｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:11.20,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry! I dropped my phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:16.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾛﾝ)あっ…ビックリした？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:16.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケータイがキズだらけで｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:16.64,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Oh, you noticed that my phone is scratched?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:17.41,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:18.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(せりか)あっ いや…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:23.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか よく落としちゃうのよね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:23.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近 手に力が入んなくて…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:21.25,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,I keep dropping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.37,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,It's like I just lose all strength in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:37.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ！そんな…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:36.89,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:41.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう いいの？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:41.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:40.52,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:41.57,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:53.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンさん…明日 朝から\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:53.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 病院へ行きましょう｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:48.43,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,Sharon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:52.43,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,you should go to a hospital again in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:57.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は神経内科へ…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:56.41,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,You should see a neurologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.49,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:10.42,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,どうこう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:10.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も…同行します｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:10.38,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,I'll accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:18.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《なんだよ…!?》\N
