Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:42.95,OP,,0,0,0,,You've always been in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:48.33,OP,,0,0,0,,But you don't say a thing or even smile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:55.42,OP,,0,0,0,,We've always been together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:02:02.18,OP,,0,0,0,,We're ignorant, but we believe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:08.48,OP,,0,0,0,,All the time I spent with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:16.90,OP,,0,0,0,,Felt like a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:24.54,OP,,0,0,0,,We connected the stars and drew pictures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:29.17,OP,,0,0,0,,To our hearts' content
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:36.72,OP,,0,0,0,,Let our hearts, shivering in excitement,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:41.51,OP,,0,0,0,,Use the sky as a canvas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:47.68,OP,,0,0,0,,And merge to form an everlasting image
