Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:43.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《ん…だめだ 集中しろ！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:43.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このテストは重要だ！➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.65,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.26,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't concentrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:45.01,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}This test is important... I should know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:47.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかってんのか!?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:47.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このテストは重要!!》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:46.78,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}This test is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:51.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《ここで いい点とって…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:51.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰よりも早く…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.83,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get a high score,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:57.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰よりも先に\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:57.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,選ばれないと だめだ!!》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:54.46,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I can hurry and reach the moon first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.17,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《でないと…》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.27,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I will reach the moon before Hibito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:06.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,⦅日々人より先に月に行って\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:06.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢シャロン望遠鏡｣を建てるよ⦆\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.30,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,And I'll build the Sharon Telescope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,⦅わかった⦆\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:09.81,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:14.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《シャロンとの約束が…》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.22,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I won't be able to keep my promise to Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンさんの病名ですが…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:23.58,Default,A,0,0,0,,We haven't been able to diagnose her disorder,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:23.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだハッキリと\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:23.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,答えは出せません｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:27.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運動神経に何らかの変化が\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:27.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生じている事は確かです｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:27.16,Default,A,0,0,0,,but there is clear evidence that her nervous system has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変化…？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.41,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:33.24,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,せいみつ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:33.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(医師)精密検査をしてもらう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:33.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必要があります｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:32.71,Default,A,0,0,0,,We will need to conduct a thorough examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンさんのご家族は？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.60,Default,A,0,0,0,,Do you have any family, Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾛﾝ)妹が２人いて\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人はニューヨークに➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.20,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Two younger sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.58,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,One is in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:42.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人は日本にいます｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.15,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,The other is in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:44.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(医師)では ここに連絡先を…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:44.63,Default,A,0,0,0,,Then, please fill in their contact information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:51.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾛﾝ)あっ…｡あれ？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.52,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:01.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(医師)あ…いいです｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:01.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が書きますので番号を…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.85,Default,A,0,0,0,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.12,Default,A,0,0,0,,Just tell me, and I'll write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…はい｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.24,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:12.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(医師)今のところ シャロンさんの\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:12.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,容体に関しては➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:12.08,Default,A,0,0,0,,At the moment, we are unable to identify
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:16.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,病名など断言できる\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:16.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,段階ではありません｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:16.29,Default,A,0,0,0,,which disorder Sharon suffers from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.84,Default,A,0,0,0,,It's possible her muscles have atrophied due to lack of exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:20.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの運動不足による筋力低下\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:20.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,というのも考えられますし…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.34,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの…私が心配しているのは\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:25.41,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,エーエルエス\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＡＬＳの可能性です｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:25.26,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,I'm concerned that it could be ALS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.44,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,When I tapped Dr. Sharon's arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:32.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロン博士の腕を叩いたら\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:32.17,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,きんせんいそくしゅうしゅく\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:32.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,筋線維束収縮の反応がありました｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:32.01,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,I observed fascicular contractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:34.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは医者？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,Are you a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:37.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４ヵ月前までは そうでした｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.76,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,I was up until four months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:41.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ ＡＬＳと\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:41.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決まったわけじゃありません｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:41.23,Default,A,0,0,0,,We still can't confirm that it's ALS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:46.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから さらに検査を続けて\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:46.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし ＡＬＳだと診断されても➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:47.21,Default,A,0,0,0,,If we run more tests and diagnose ALS,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:50.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,段階的に\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:50.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伝えていく必要があります｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:50.03,Default,A,0,0,0,,we'll need to break the news to her slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:55.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても…重い病気ですので｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:54.08,Default,A,0,0,0,,It's a very serious disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:58.04,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}A serious disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:58.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《重い病気…》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:12.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は ありがとう｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:12.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妹が来てくれることになったわ｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:09.79,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.22,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,My sister's on her way over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:15.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 心配しないで\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:15.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,訓練 頑張ってね｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.17,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,So don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:17.21,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Just focus on training, Mutta and Serika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムッタ せりかさん｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:19.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜いくつもの\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:19.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,検査予定を告げられ…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.85,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}After multiple tests were scheduled,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:19.85,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:22.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が何らかの病気である事は➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:23.73,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sharon must have realized that she had a serious disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:25.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンにも\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:25.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかっていただろうが…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:28.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女は笑顔をやめなかった＞\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:28.75,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she never stopped smiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せりかさん…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.54,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Serika,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:42.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何なの？…ＡＬＳって？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:42.50,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,what is ALS?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:54.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の父が亡くなった病気です｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.68,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,It's the disease that killed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:02.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手の力が うまく入らなかったり\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:02.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,転ぶ事が多くなったり➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:07:00.54,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,Your arms suddenly feel weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.78,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,You begin to trip over yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:07.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロン博士の症状が…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:07.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりに父と似てたので…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:06.65,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,Sharon was displaying the same symptoms as my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:14.81,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,The disorder affects your motor neurons,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:14.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運動ニューロンっていう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:14.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神経だけが障害を受けて➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:20.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脳から筋肉を動かす命令が\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:20.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伝わらなくなっていくんです｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:19.29,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,meaning that your muscles stop moving when your brain tells them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:25.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのせいで 筋肉がやせて\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:25.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,徐々に手足が動かせなくなって➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.80,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,As a result, your muscles weaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:25.24,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,Eventually, you can no longer move your arms or legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:29.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食べることも 話すことも…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.59,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,You become unable to talk, eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自力で呼吸も\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できなくなってしまいます｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:32.32,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,or breathe unassisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:41.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《シャロンが…》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:39.56,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sharon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:44.44,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Now, try playing the trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:45.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,⦅さあ トランペットを持って\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:45.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,音を出して⦆\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:49.66,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,きじ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,⦅しばらく 生地をねかせたら\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これの登場よ！⦆\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.61,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,After kneading for a while, switch to these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:55.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,⦅ムッタは何でもできる\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:55.03,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,すご\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:55.03,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,あにき\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:55.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,凄い兄貴になりたかったのよ⦆\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:54.24,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Mutta wanted to become an amazing big brother who could do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《あの シャロンが…》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.98,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not Sharon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:16.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《くそっ！…わかんねぇな…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.66,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.79,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:21.44,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I read the manuals, but I can't remember a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと訓練教材\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,読んだつもりが➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然 頭に\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入ってねぇじゃねぇか!!➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け…！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンのことは今 考えるな！》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.48,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.72,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't think about Sharon right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:40.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,⦅ＡＬＳは人によって\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:40.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,進行の速さも違って…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:41.04,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,ALS progression varies from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:44.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１０年以上かけて\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:44.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,徐々に悪化する人もいれば➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:44.79,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,Some people may go ten years before symptoms worsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:48.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の父のように\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:48.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,速い人もいます⦆\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:48.40,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,But for some, like my father, it's much faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:53.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,⦅は…速いって？⦆\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.59,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,H-How fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,⦅父は診断されてから➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:58.89,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,After my father's diagnosis, he lived for two years, ten months before passing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:59.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２年と１０ヵ月で\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:59.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,亡くなりました⦆\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:06.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ビンス)試験終了です｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:06.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ペンを置いて下さい｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:06.31,Default,Vin,0,0,0,,The test is over. Put your pens down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:12.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪終わった～！≫\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:10.19,Default,Shane,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:18.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《ちくしょう…！》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:15.68,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:22.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜テストの結果は…最悪だった＞\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:22.31,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}My test scores were terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:33.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[TV](拍手)\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.44,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,ひびと\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(南波日々人)ハァ…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:32.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜シャロンの検査から８日後…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.32,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eight days after her examination ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:38.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＡＬＳという診断結果が\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:38.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,医師から彼女に告げられた＞\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:38.41,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}the doctors told Sharon she had ALS.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:49.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾛﾝ)田村さんたちが\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:49.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日本で待ってるからね｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:49.04,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Tamura and the other astronomers are waiting in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:53.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も帰って\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:53.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月面望遠鏡の計画を進めるわ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:53.06,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,I have to go back and work on our plan to build the lunar telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:57.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…ああ…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:57.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも あんま無理はしないでよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:57.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おばちゃん｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.59,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:57.57,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,But don't work too hard, Aunt Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞けば\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せりかちゃんの お父さんも➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:04.87,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Serika told me her father continued to research until he lost all ability to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:04.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体が動かなくなるギリギリまで\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:04.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,研究を続けたらしいのよね｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:09.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も見習って\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:09.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くとこまで行くわよ！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.68,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,I'll follow his example, and do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:14.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜医師は彼女に ちゃんと病気の\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:14.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,説明をしたのだろうか？➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:13.95,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did the doctors do a proper job of explaining her disorder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:18.05,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was so positive, I had to wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:18.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう疑うほど\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:18.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンは陽気だった｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:21.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと数ヵ月で シャロンは➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:23.43,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a few months, Sharon will no longer be able to play the piano anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:24.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大好きなピアノも\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:24.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弾けなくなってしまう｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:27.76,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}The doctors must have told her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:27.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その事を医師から\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:27.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,告げられているはずなのに…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:32.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも彼女は笑っていた＞\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.95,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she continued to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:41.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロン！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.44,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:45.95,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,It'll probably take three or four years before this will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:45.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３年先か４年先か\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:45.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかんね～けど 俺の中じゃ➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が誰より先に選ばれて\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月で望遠鏡を建てる予定だよ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:51.99,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,But I plan to be the first one chosen to go to the moon and build your telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:13:00.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがと 楽しみにしてる｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.08,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:59.58,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{part b}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:20.69,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hey, Aunt Sharon... Tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ シャロンおばちゃん\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えて…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢僕は いざという時\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,役にも立たない➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:28.32,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,How do I say, "I'm a useless person who always fails during crunch time," in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:28.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメ人間です｣って\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:28.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,英語で何て言うの？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何それ？そんなの訊いて\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうするの？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.73,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.33,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:36.03,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I'll need to know when I make friends in other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:36.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつか 外国の友達ができたら\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:36.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うんだよ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:38.92,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Since I'll probably be saying it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:39.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか俺 よく使いそうだから｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かあったの？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:40.98,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:43.88,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:43.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいからぁ～ 教えてって！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.34,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:50.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうね…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 ムッタが言った文の\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,英訳じゃないんだけど➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:58.90,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,This doesn't mean the exact same thing, but it's a simple phrase you can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:14:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとシンプルな\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:14:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い回しがあるわ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:08.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾛﾝ)はい これ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.15,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:11.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え～と イッツ ア…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:11.12,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Uh, "It's..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.40,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,イッツ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.40,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,ピース\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.40,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,オブ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.40,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,ケイク\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾛﾝ)“It's a piece of cake"｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.96,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,It's a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:19.22,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,ひと\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:19.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを直訳すれば｢ケｰキ一切れ分｣\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:19.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,って事になるんだけどね｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:20.79,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,And the phrase "piece of cake" also has a completely different meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:23.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う意味もあるのよ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:27.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど…｢僕はケーキ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:27.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一切れ分の価値しかない➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.17,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:30.72,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,It means I'm a useless human, worth less than a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:30.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっけないダメ人間です｣\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:30.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,って意味か｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:34.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふっ…まあ そうね｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.61,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:37.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自由に使っていいわよ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.34,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,Say that whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:41.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現在 \N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:15:01.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《料理…裁縫…文字を書く…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:01.02,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cooking, sewing, writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:07.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,細かな手作業から\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:07.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できなくなっていく…か…》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:06.21,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,{\i1}It begins with the loss of any ability requiring hand coordination...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:12.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ～ なんてヘタな字…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.47,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,My handwriting's so ugly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何の根拠もなく\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,口から出まかせを…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:47.18,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I was lying out of my ass back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:52.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:52.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢誰より先に月へ行く｣だよ！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:51.76,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I'll be chosen to go to the moon before anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:59.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンを安心させるつもりで\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:59.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ～言ったんだろ？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.64,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that to comfort Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンの別れ際の笑顔も\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ～いう事だろうよ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:04.15,Default,HI,0,0,0,,That's why she was smiling when she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:11.58,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,ティー\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:11.58,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,さんぱち\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:11.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 Ｔ－３８の筆記テストで\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:11.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最低点だった…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:10.58,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I had the lowest score on the T-38 written test.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:18.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで出遅れた奴は\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:18.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,宇宙まで１０年待つって噂だ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:16.33,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I've heard you have to wait ten years to reach space if you fall behind here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:20.21,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:23.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《チクショー…こんな大事な時に\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:23.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果を出せねぇ…》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.79,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never produce results when I need them most!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:27.00,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a useless person who always fails during crunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:27.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《いざという時\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:27.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,役にも立たないダメ人間…！》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰がどのタイミングでミｯションに\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アサインされるのかは➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:33.52,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Honestly, I have no idea how they decide when and who they assign to each mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正直 俺にも\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかんね～けどさ…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:39.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし 筆記テストの点数順が\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:39.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アサイン順になるってんなら➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:39.03,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,But if written test scores were a factor,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.52,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I doubt I'd have gotten to go to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:43.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はまだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:43.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,宇宙に行ってないと思わん？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:59.53,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sharon's disease will rob her of the ability to use her hands and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:17:01.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《シャロンの病気は いずれ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:17:01.41,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,うば\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:17:01.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンの手足の自由を奪う》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:04.53,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll be able to hear, but not talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:06.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《耳は聞こえるけど\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:06.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話せなくなる》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:07.83,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll be able to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《目は見えるけど まぶたを\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開く事ができなくなってしまう》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.11,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}but not to open her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:17.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《そうなる前に俺は…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:17.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見せられんのか!?》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:16.83,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I make it up there before that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《シャロンの見たがってる\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小惑星の姿を…!!》\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:21.29,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}To show her the asteroid she wants to see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.90,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,Oh? Are you alone today, Nanba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ？今日は\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとりなんですか？南波さん｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ せりかさん…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.78,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Serika...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:20.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんかまだ みんなでわいわい\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:20.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食べれる気分じゃなくてさ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.96,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood to eat with everyone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかります｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.28,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:25.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ていうか せりかさん\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:25.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お昼 それ１個？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.24,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Wait, Serika...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.66,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Is that all you're having for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:29.61,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,No, this is more along the lines of dessert...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:30.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え あ いや…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:30.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食後の別腹というやつです｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“It's a piece of cake"って英語\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使った事ある？せりかさん｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:39.51,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Have you ever used the phrase, "It's a piece of cake"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:45.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん…いえ ないですけど\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:45.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味は知ってますよ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.53,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,No, I haven't,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.22,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,but I know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:49.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“楽勝だよ"って事ですよね｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:48.48,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,It means that something is easy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう…“楽勝だよ"｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.39,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Yes, that it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:19:02.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昔 シャロンが 教えて\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:19:02.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くれたんだけどさ この言葉｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:59.35,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,A long time ago, Sharon taught me that phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:07.18,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I was actually requesting a self-derogatory English phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:04.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも そん時 本当は➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:08.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとネガティブなセリフの\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:08.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,英訳を頼んだんだ｡そしたら…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.08,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:11.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,⦅“It's a piece of cake"⦆\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.42,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,It's a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:14.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,って 堂々とウソを！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.24,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,She lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:20.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 本当の意味は\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:20.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,高校ん時に知ったワケだけど➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.12,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Well, I learned the real meaning in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.51,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,But yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:24.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも あれだ…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:24.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ～いうウソなら➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:28.31,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Sharon's the kind of person who's willing to lie in that situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:29.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,平気でついちゃう人なんだよな\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:29.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンって…｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:37.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月面望遠鏡の約束の事\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:37.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンさんから聞きましたよ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:37.40,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,Sharon told me about your promise to build a telescope on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.23,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,とうじょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私がＩＳＳ搭乗を希望するのは➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:48.82,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,I want to board the ISS to be able to develop new treatments for incurable diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:49.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,難病に効く新薬開発に\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:49.72,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,こうけん\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:49.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貢献するためです｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特に…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の父を苦しめたＡＬＳを➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:56.26,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,In particular, I wish to rid the world of ALS, the disease that took my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:59.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世から\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:59.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なくしてしまいたいんです｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:08.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も…シャロンさんと\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:08.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約束したんです｡自信もないのに｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:03.32,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,I also made a promise to Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.23,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,I'm not very confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:15.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャロンさんの病気に効く薬を\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:15.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が生み出してみせるって｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:14.11,Default,Seri,0,0,0,,But I promised to develop a medicine to help treat Sharon's disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:38.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜翌朝 シャロンから\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:38.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メールが届いた＞\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:38.21,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next morning, I received an e-mail from Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:43.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢無事 日本に到着です｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:43.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は明日から 張り切って➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:41.19,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made it back to Japan safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:47.89,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Starting tomorrow, I'll work on manuals for constructing a telescope on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:48.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月面望遠鏡の製作手順書を\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:48.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,作っていきます｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:52.82,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,{\i1}So don't worry... Just focus on your training, Mutta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:53.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の事は心配しないで\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:53.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,訓練 頑張ってね ムッタ｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:57.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も ３年後か４年後かに…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:57.73,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,{\i1}In three or four years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:03.43,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I plan to head over, to brief you on the lunar telescope project.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:04.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたに 月面望遠鏡計画の全ての\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:04.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,説明を伝えに行く予定です｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えることだらけよ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚悟はいい？｣｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.80,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll have a lot to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.56,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:37.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ってくれるじゃないの ムッタ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.47,Default,Sharon,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the spirit, Mutta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:46.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜シャロンを\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:46.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,元気づけられるような文章は➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:49.30,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}After racking my brain for the words to cheer Sharon up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:52.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えても考えても生み出せず…➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ケーキ一切れ分"とだけ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,返信した＞\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:56.64,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could only respond with a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:15.97,ED,,0,0,0,,As you place your hopes on the distant moon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:20.27,ED,,0,0,0,,And leave on your journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:26.53,ED,,0,0,0,,You smile in spite of your loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:30.78,ED,,0,0,0,,Because you believe in yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:37.70,ED,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if your wings don't match
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:41.46,ED,,0,0,0,,Spread them out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.08,ED,,0,0,0,,As you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:49.26,ED,,0,0,0,,begin your long journey (try now) (try now)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:53.97,ED,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can make it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:59.85,ED,,0,0,0,,Please don't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:02.98,ED,,0,0,0,,to move straight forward
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.31,0:23:04.94,ED,,0,0,0,,You took
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:11.36,ED,,0,0,0,,all your pain and sorrow (no more) (no more)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:15.78,ED,,0,0,0,,And turned it into your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.78,0:23:22.04,ED,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure even your destiny to fight many a battle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:24.96,ED,,0,0,0,,Is on your side
