Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:38.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,操縦訓練が始まる＞\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:40.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜私の訓練教官として\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:40.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現れたのは➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:42.40,preview,Mu,0,0,0,,And I end up with that old guy as my instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あろうことか\N
