Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:44.61,preview,D,0,0,0,,Good to see you again, Mutta!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:44.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞﾆｰﾙ)＜久しぶりだな ムッタ＞\N
